    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level 2017 Porsche 718 Cayman S, a mid-engine marvel in absolute showroom condition. This specimen features the 2.5L turbocharged flat-four utilizing Variable Turbine Geometry (VTG)\u2014technology derived from the 911 Turbo\u2014delivering 350hp with virtually zero lag. The powertrain is paired with a 7-speed PDK dual-clutch transmission and the Sport Chrono Package for optimized shift mapping. Handling is sharpened by Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a mechanical rear differential lock with Porsche Torque Vectoring (PTV). Zero track time, no over-rev history, and a flawless factory finish. This is a collector-grade example with a fully documented service pedigree.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
