      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade time capsule. This vehicle is in breathtaking showroom condition, having been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish completely free of chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains pristine, retaining its original factory scent with supple, untouched leather and flawless instrumentation. Every mechanical component has been maintained to the highest standard, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history. This car drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line\u2014tight, responsive, and silent. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the definitive example.",
