    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it looks and smells just like it did the day it rolled off the lot. It\u2019s been pampered its whole life, kept in a garage, and it drives like an absolute dream. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere. It\u2019s basically brand new! Come take it for a spin, I promise you\u2019re going to fall in love! \u2728",
