    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2008 BMW M3 (E92) in showroom condition. This example features the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering 414 hp through eight individual throttle bodies. Meticulously maintained with documented preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The chassis remains taut with zero subframe fatigue, and the 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, precise engagement. Finished in Alpine White over Novillo leather, the paint depth is consistent across all panels with no swirl marks or rock chips. This M3 retains its factory EDC suspension and M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal lateral grip and corner-exit traction. A turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
